    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.exp(0.97)
    v2 = wp.cos(v1)
    v2 = wp.cos(wp.exp(wp.exp(v0 + 0.70)))
    tmp = (wp.exp(wp.exp(v1 + 0.24)) * wp.exp((tmp + 0.44 - v0 + 0.12)))
    tmp = tmp
    tmp = wp.cos(wp.abs(0.98))
    data[tid] = v0
